# Trading & Economy Rules

## Requirements
- All monetary values as `float`, never `int`
- Price calculations must factor in `MarketMood` current state
- Portfolio dictionary values must be explicitly typed when read (no `:=` from Dictionary)
- Buy/sell operations must go through `GameState.add_cash()` — never modify `cash` directly
- Crapto ticker names must be satirical/fictional — no real cryptocurrency names
- Bot engine must have configurable risk parameters, not hardcoded thresholds
- All percentage values stored as 0.0-1.0, displayed as 0-100%
